          "reviewBody": "I have known Gurukul The School Crossings Republik campus for almost 05 years now, it's led by few of the most experienced leaders from education sector, who know well about crafting a detailed, in depth growth curriculum for students. I am delighted to see the pattern followed to educate students which is not limited to books and routine tasks, it takes care of overall improvement of today's kids wherein they are well equipped to take up challenges in the adulthood. My best wishes to the school management and entire support staff. You have created benchmarks that others would like to follow. Highly recommend for admission from the very beginning so that growth trajectory is well defined. Regards.",
